{"tid":825524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"同消防警察對比圖中嘅走佬警察平反","createTime":"2018-09-17T15:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T10:32:03.000Z","uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f7cc9f75d583b5a3efabc584a575c27262769457","tid":825524,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:25:19.000Z","msg":"同消防警察對比圖中嘅走佬警察平反<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳幅圖，消防員衝入火場，而警察就畀人描述為走佬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/232157_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F232157_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d2a2d117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實原片係咁嘅，由20秒開始<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WAxPOMSYEZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWAxPOMSYEZQ&d=qaGD6MXvZF4JfdaeeQTXPpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=825734f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WAxPOMSYEZQ</a><br />\n<br />\n其實佢係叫緊在場圍觀嘅記者同市民走，因為驚會再爆炸<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好再誤會佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係圖可以照貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d85a2271c82e4fac2aa03a5a5a628a664bf7819","tid":825524,"uid":36296,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"懷疑樓主=片中警犬"},{"pid":"9b53f57f7ebf4ec64f8864626aa71fb34ece6150","tid":825524,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1d85a2271c82e4fac2aa03a5a5a628a664bf7819","tid":825524,"uid":36296,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"懷疑樓主=片中警犬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"我靚仔過佢好多<img src=\"/ass